OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA bright end
OL,6,Fto the day with any showers dying out.
OL,7,FStaying mainly dry overnight but cloud
OL,8,Fwill increase from the west with a
OL,9,Flittle light rain in places.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTuesday:FAny early light rain clearing
OL,12,Fthen a mainly dry and bright morning.
OL,13,FA cloudier afternoon with heavy
OL,14,Fshowers or longer spells of rain
OL,15,Fdeveloping.
