OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FA
OL,6,Fsunny start to Wednesday then heavy
OL,7,Fshowers developing. Mainly dry and
OL,8,Fcloudy on Thursday, perhaps a little
OL,9,Frain later..Sunshine and showers
OL,10,Flikely on Friday.
